This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) as it proposes a novel few-shot learning method using meta-learning and transfer learning. The paper also conducts experiments on image recognition tasks, which suggests it could also belong to computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper involves training deep neural networks, which could place it in the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), or neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
